# tkv2 — the reduced busi home screen (integration bar for slices 1–4)

Slice `tkv2-busi-home-conformance` of `specs/ssc-toolkit-v2.md`: the shapes
busi's real home screen needs — an obligations list with per-item
instance-scoped expand state, an income form with validators-as-data, and an
offline-cached home payload — exercised together, INT==JS.

[Ctx, component, ctxSignal, ctxName](std/ui/component.ssc)
[field, form, draft, formErrors, formValid](std/ui/form.ssc)
[localStorageGet, localStorageSet, persistedSignal, onlineSignal](std/ui/offline.ssc)

```scalascript
// ── Obligations: busi-shaped ids, one expand signal per card ─────────────
case class Ob(id: String, title: String, amount: String)
val obs = [
  Ob("pit-28/2026-07", "PIT-28 advance", "1200"),
  Ob("zus/2026-07", "ZUS social", "1600"),
  Ob("health/2026-07", "Skladka zdrowotna", "461")
]

def expandSignal(o: Ob): Any =
  component("obCard", o.id)(ctx => ctxSignal(ctx, "expanded", false))

val expands = obs.map(o => expandSignal(o))
println(expands.length)

// ids sanitize to distinct JS-safe names
println(obs.map(o => component("obCard", o.id)(ctx => ctxName(ctx, "expanded"))).mkString(","))

// expanding one card never touches the others
expands.head.set(true)
println(expands.map(e => e()).mkString(","))

// ── Income form: amount digits-only + date shape, gate flips live ────────
val f = component("income", "home")(ctx => form(ctx, [
  field("amount", label = "Amount", required = true, pattern = "[0-9]+(\\.[0-9]{1,2})?",
        patternMsg = "digits only"),
  field("date", label = "Date", required = true, pattern = "[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}",
        patternMsg = "YYYY-MM-DD")
]))
val valid = formValid(f)
println(valid())

draft(f, "amount").set("not-a-number")
draft(f, "date").set("2026-07-07")
println(formErrors(f)())
println(valid())

draft(f, "amount").set("3500.00")
println(formErrors(f)())
println(valid())

// ── Offline home cache: last payload survives via storage ────────────────
val home = persistedSignal("busiLastHome", "{}")
println(home())
home.set("{\"cash\":\"12000\",\"attention\":1}")
println(localStorageGet("busiLastHome"))

// a fresh signal for the same key sees the cached payload (reload shape)
val homeAfterReload = persistedSignal("busiLastHome", "{}")
println(homeAfterReload())

// online flag readable (constant true off-browser)
println(onlineSignal()())
```
